---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---
<ServiceLayout
  title="Contact Websites by Luca Kosowski"
  description="Contact Luca Kosowski directly for simple, clear, reliable website inquiries. Email or LinkedIn; no form required."
  canonicalPath="/contact/"
  ogTitle="Contact Websites by Luca Kosowski"
  ogDescription="Start a website inquiry directly with Luca Kosowski by email or LinkedIn. No form, no funnel, just a clear first message."
>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>

  <header class="showcase-topbar showcase-topbar--static" aria-label="Website contact navigation">
    <a href="https://lucakosowski.com/" class="identity">Luca Kosowski</a>
    <nav aria-label="Contact page links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/approach/">Approach</a>
      <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main id="main" class="contact-route" tabindex="-1">
    <section class="scope-note decision-note contact-page-card" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">Direct website inquiry</p>
      <h1 id="contact-title">Contact Websites by Luca</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Start with a direct message. No form, no funnel, no questionnaire — just the context for the website you need and the best way to reply.</p>

      <div class="decision-grid contact-method-grid" aria-label="Contact methods">
        <article>
          <strong>Email</strong>
          <span><a href="mailto:hello@lucakosowski.com" data-goatcounter-click="contact-email-service-contact" data-goatcounter-title="Contact email click — service contact">hello@lucakosowski.com</a></span>
        </article>

        <article>
          <strong>LinkedIn</strong>
          <span><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luca-kosowski/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-goatcounter-click="contact-linkedin-service-contact" data-goatcounter-title="Contact LinkedIn click — service contact">linkedin.com/in/luca-kosowski</a></span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="scope-note decision-note contact-page-card contact-page-card--quiet" aria-labelledby="message-title">
      <p class="eyebrow">What to send</p>
      <h2 id="message-title">A useful first message is short</h2>
      <div class="decision-grid decision-grid--steps" aria-label="First message checklist">
        <article>
          <strong>What you need</strong>
          <span>For example: a one-page business site, a digital business card, a service page, or a cleaner version of an existing website.</span>
        </article>
        <article>
          <strong>What already exists</strong>
          <span>Send any current website, brand material, text, photos, examples you like, or business pages that explain the offer.</span>
        </article>
        <article>
          <strong>What matters most</strong>
          <span>Tell me whether the priority is trust, speed, clarity, style, proof, local discovery, or a simple contact path.</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</ServiceLayout>
